ygData.msgSnippet: Um...Kristin...there s another room in the guild. Through the inner doors, are two more song merchants. They have the 8 and 9th level songs.
ygData.messageBody:
Um...Kristin...there's another room in the guild. Through the inner doors, are two
more song merchants. They have the 8 and 9th level songs.
